                            <comment id="460752" author="adilger" created="Fri, 20 Jun 2025 22:03:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=laisiyao&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;laisiyao&quot;&gt;laisiyao&lt;/a&gt;, it probably makes sense to change the version check to exclude all rhel 9.x kernels, like:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
       &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; [[ &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;$CLIENT_OS_ID_LIKE&quot;&lt;/span&gt; =~ &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;rhel&quot;&lt;/span&gt; ]]; then
               &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (( $CLIENT_OS_VERSION_CODE &amp;gt;= $(version_code 9.0) &amp;amp;&amp;amp;
                     $CLIENT_OS_VERSION_CODE &amp;lt;= $(version_code 9.100) )); then
                       echo &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;stat $DIR/$tdir to cache it in el9.x&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
                       stat $DIR/$tdir
               fi
       fi
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
